not change my voice. Nothin'.

24:57.184 --> 24:58.913
Okay. Sounds good.

24:58.985 --> 25:00.213
Uh, let's start.

25:00.287 --> 25:01.379
Okay.

25:02.989 --> 25:04.616
You're gonna talk like that
the whole time?

25:04.691 --> 25:06.022
Yes.

25:06.092 --> 25:07.116
You know what?

25:07.194 --> 25:09.560
I'm still picking up a slight
bit of emotion from you...

25:09.629 --> 25:10.857
so what I think
we should do...

25:10.931 --> 25:14.628
is turn our chairs back to back
so I can't see you at all.

25:14.701 --> 25:15.725
- Okay.
- Okay?

25:21.474 --> 25:23.066
- Better?
- Yes.

25:24.144 --> 25:25.111
You know what?

25:25.178 --> 25:27.305
To be safe, I think we should be
in separate rooms.

25:27.380 --> 25:29.371
Oh, but then
I'm gonna have to shout.

25:29.449 --> 25:31.417
Yeah, all right. Now you're
just messing with me, right?

25:33.486 --> 25:34.976
Yes.

25:35.055 --> 25:37.023
That's pretty stupid, huh?

25:37.090 --> 25:38.114
Yes.

25:38.191 --> 25:39.283
You wanna
go get something to eat?

25:39.359 --> 25:40.383
Yes.

25:44.464 --> 25:46.455
So, you bring
all your psychics here?

25:46.533 --> 25:48.160
Well, you really should know
the answer to that.

25:49.803 --> 25:51.498
But this is a cool place
that you picked...

25:51.571 --> 25:52.538
I'll give you that.

25:52.606 --> 25:54.130
Kate showed it to me.

25:59.079 --> 26:00.706
You know,
I'm getting the feeling...

26:00.780 --> 26:02.941
like she wants you
to be happy again...

26:03.016 --> 26:04.711
like when you used to come here.

26:06.019 --> 26:07.577
I'm getting that feeling, too.

26:18.198 --> 26:19.927
You are so screwed.

26:20.000 --> 26:21.968
- What?
- I didn't say anything.

26:22.869 --> 26:25.099
Oh. Right.

26:29.209 --> 26:30.233
Traitors.

26:30.310 --> 26:33.871
Lying, cheating,
red-headed hussy.

26:33.947 --> 26:35.141
I'll wring her neck.

26:36.449 --> 26:39.907
Throw her in front of a car,
throw her down some stairs.

26:39.986 --> 26:42.978
# She had blonde hair,
blue eyes, too #

26:43.056 --> 26:45.024
# And she had
a little itty-bitty #

26:45.091 --> 26:46.615
# Hootchie-cootchie-coo #

26:46.693 --> 26:48.524
You. You bastard.

26:48.595 --> 26:50.563
Whoa. Hey, evening, Miss.

26:51.464 --> 26:52.431
You can hear me?

26:52.499 --> 26:53.659
Unfortunately.

26:53.733 --> 26:54.700
Are you psychic?

26:54.768 --> 26:56.030
No, dead.

26:56.636 --> 26:58.069
Good. What happened?

26:58.138 --> 27:00.038
Drunk driving accident.

27:00.106 --> 27:01.903
Oh, so backing over me
with your truck wasn't enough...

27:01.975 --> 27:03.670
to get you to stop
drinking and driving?

27:03.743 --> 27:04.971
I'm not proud.

27:05.045 --> 27:06.103
What are you doing here?

27:06.179 --> 27:07.305
Same as you.

27:07.380 --> 27:10.645
Takin' care
of unfinished business.

27:10.717 --> 27:11.911
Are you sure
that's why you're here?

27:11.985 --> 27:13.247
That's what the lady told me.

27:13.320 --> 27:14.912
- The lady in the white room?
- 'Course.

27:14.988 --> 27:16.387
Why, what'd she tell you?

27:16.456 --> 27:17.480
None of your business.

27:18.325 --> 27:19.792
Did she give you any hints?

27:19.859 --> 27:21.622
How... How specific was she?

27:22.829 --> 27:24.922
Ah, you didn't talk to her,
did you?

27:25.865 --> 27:27.264
What'd you do, piss her off?

27:27.334 --> 27:28.631
Unfinished business.

27:31.438 --> 27:32.462
Well, that's it.

27:33.974 --> 27:35.498
I got to protect Henry.

27:35.575 --> 27:36.599
Yeah.

27:36.676 --> 27:38.371
Wh... Hey, hey!

27:39.646 --> 27:40.670
You're welcome.

27:44.250 --> 27:46.150
Hey. Can I help you?

27:46.219 --> 27:47.516
Hi. Um, I'm sorry.

27:47.587 --> 27:48.781
I called, and no one answered.

27:48.855 --> 27:51.688
Um, my friend gave me
your number in yoga class.

27:51.758 --> 27:53.350
Well, I'm just having
a really bad day.

27:53.426 --> 27:56.884
My... My friend died,
and we had a fight.

27:56.963 --> 27:59.625
Oh, okay, okay.
Sure, sure, sure, come in.

27:59.699 --> 28:00.927
Come in. It's fine.

28:01.001 --> 28:02.263
Thank you.

28:03.970 --> 28:06.097
Okay. Come right this way.

28:08.375 --> 28:10.002
I'm sorry,
I didn't catch your name.

28:10.076 --> 28:12.544
Oh, it's Kay... eleen.

28:12.612 --> 28:14.102
- Kayleen?
- Mm-hmm.

28:14.180 --> 28:15.772
Great.
Um, why don't you come this way.

28:15.849 --> 28:16.975
Uh, just have a seat.

28:17.050 --> 28:19.041
Do you want a drink or anything?

28:19.119 --> 28:20.086
No, I'm fine.

28:20.153 --> 28:21.120
Okay, great.

28:21.187 --> 28:22.984
Make yourself comfortable.

28:24.257 --> 28:25.622
Okay.

28:27.694 --> 28:29.127
So, you talk to dead people?

28:29.195 --> 28:31.288
Well, I can't promise results...

28:31.364 --> 28:33.355
but, yes,
I have had some success.

28:33.433 --> 28:35.424
Comes in nice and clear, huh?

28:35.502 --> 28:36.469
No mistaking it?

28:36.536 --> 28:37.696
Sometimes, yeah.

28:37.771 --> 28:38.829
Great. Can't wait.

28:38.905 --> 28:40.167
All right, so the first thing
I'm gonna have you do...

28:40.240 --> 28:41.434
is give me your hands.

28:41.508 --> 28:43.533
Uh, you...
Uh, we probably shouldn't...

28:43.610 --> 28:45.874
because I'm, uh,
coming down with a cold.

28:52.652 --> 28:55.553
Okay. Um, great.

28:55.622 --> 28:56.919
Okay, this is what
we'll do then.

28:56.990 --> 29:00.619
Um, why don't you concentrate
on your friend, okay?

29:00.693 --> 29:02.786
And let's try to see
if she can come through to us.

29:02.862 --> 29:04.557
- You're the psychic.
- Great.

29:11.171 --> 29:13.332
Yeah, wow,
I'm getting something.

29:13.406 --> 29:17.365
Ashley Clark, you have made
a mockery of the gifts...

29:17.444 --> 29:18.934
you've been given.

29:19.012 --> 29:20.980
Uh, Kayleen?

29:21.047 --> 29:23.515
You speak falsely for the dead.

29:23.583 --> 29:26.552
We have been sent here
to give you a warning.

29:26.619 --> 29:30.646
Stop now or suffer
a terrible fate.

29:30.723 --> 29:32.156
Is this some sort of joke?

29:32.225 --> 29:33.556
This is no joke.

29:33.626 --> 29:36.561
We see and hear everything.

29:36.629 --> 29:40.190
We saw you drop the tray
of meatballs last night...

29:40.266 --> 29:42.530
and still serve them.

29:42.602 --> 29:45.628
We saw what you did
in the shower last night...

29:46.539 --> 29:48.404
and it's nothing
to be ashamed of...

29:48.475 --> 29:50.773
but we still saw.

29:50.844 --> 29:52.744
And we see
what you're trying to do...

29:52.812 --> 29:54.302
to Henry Mills.

29:54.380 --> 29:56.314
I... I'm just...

29:56.382 --> 29:57.508
You, of all people...

29:57.584 --> 30:00.451
should know the consequences
of defaming the dead.

30:00.520 --> 30:02.454
Leave Henry Mills alone...

30:02.522 --> 30:05.252
or you will never
find peace again.

30:05.325 --> 30:08.590
You will lose your possessions,
your friends...

30:08.661 --> 30:12.028
and eventually your life.

30:12.098 --> 30:16.125
This is the only time
we will visit you.

30:21.808 --> 30:24.208
Oh, I must've dozed off.

30:24.277 --> 30:25.801
Did you contact my friend?

30:26.946 --> 30:28.277
Ashley, are you okay?

30:30.884 --> 30:31.873
Please go.

30:31.951 --> 30:33.976
Well, you look
like you've seen a ghost.

30:34.053 --> 30:36.248
Can you go now, please?

30:36.322 --> 30:37.346
Just go.

30:57.443 --> 30:58.842
You'll never guess
who I ran into.

30:58.912 --> 31:00.174
- Who?
- Ashley.

31:01.481 --> 31:02.880
Ashley...

31:02.949 --> 31:04.541
I know so many Ashleys.

31:04.617 --> 31:05.584
The psychic.

31:05.652 --> 31:07.745
Oh, that Ashley.

31:07.820 --> 31:09.811
- What did she say?
- Well, it was really weird.

31:09.889 --> 31:13.552
I mean, she got these images,
really specific stuff.

31:13.626 --> 31:15.355
Really? Wow.

31:15.428 --> 31:16.554
Will she get a message
from Kate?

31:17.730 --> 31:19.391
- Like what?
- Huh?

31:19.465 --> 31:20.830
- What?
- What?

31:21.801 --> 31:24.929
Anyway, we're, you know,
gonna try it again.

31:25.004 --> 31:26.767
That's great.
That's... I really...

31:26.839 --> 31:28.431
I feel like
she can help you, Henry.

31:28.975 --> 31:30.533
Come on, Ashley!

31:32.078 --> 31:33.443
Ashley, come on!

31:33.513 --> 31:35.037
She's not home?

31:36.182 --> 31:38.275
Uh, why?

31:38.351 --> 31:39.375
Are you here to meet her?

31:39.452 --> 31:41.317
No, we had, um, an appointment.

31:41.387 --> 31:43.116
Wait a second.
Are you Henry...

31:43.189 --> 31:44.850
the-the veterinarian?

31:44.924 --> 31:46.118
She mentioned me?

31:46.192 --> 31:47.454
No, it's just
a really lucky guess.

31:47.527 --> 31:48.926
I'm good like that.

31:48.995 --> 31:50.428
I'm Dan, the catering partner.

31:50.496 --> 31:51.895
- Right. Hi, Dan.
- Hi.

31:51.965 --> 31:53.592
Yeah, we were supposed to meet
an hour and a half ago...

31:53.666 --> 31:55.930
at this restaurant, but
she's not answering her phone.

31:56.002 --> 31:57.731
I know.
I've been calling her all day.

31:57.804 --> 31:58.828
Do you mind if I try?

31:59.706 --> 32:01.333
Knocking?

32:01.407 --> 32:04.205
Please. No, please.
Help yourself.

32:04.277 --> 32:06.177
Maybe later you can come
jab an elevator button...

32:06.246 --> 32:07.907
a hundred times
after I've already pushed it.

32:10.550 --> 32:11.517
Ashley!

32:11.584 --> 32:13.745
Ashley, it's Henry.
Are you there?

32:14.787 --> 32:16.516
Henry, I'm sick!

32:16.589 --> 32:19.149
I tried to call.

32:19.225 --> 32:21.523
I might be sick
for a really long time.

32:22.962 --> 32:24.327
Okay, do you need anything?

32:24.397 --> 32:27.958
No. I'll call you
if I ever feel better.

32:28.034 --> 32:29.365
Ashley?

32:30.003 --> 32:31.129
Ashley!

32:35.108 --> 32:36.336
Got more than you did.

32:40.613 --> 32:43.013
Hey, it's Ashley,
psychic-slash-caterer...

32:43.082 --> 32:44.413
leave an awesome message.

32:44.484 --> 32:46.042
Good morning. It's Henry.

32:46.119 --> 32:47.677
Just thought I'd check in
since you didn't...

32:47.754 --> 32:48.706
# This little light of mine #

32:48.707 --> 32:50.314
sound so good last night,
see if you're all right.

32:50.390 --> 32:53.587
- So, um, you all right?
- # I'm gonna let it shine #

32:53.660 --> 32:54.957
Morning again.

32:55.028 --> 32:56.859
It's, uh, Henry again.

32:56.929 --> 32:58.829
That's some cold.
I hope you didn't get it...

32:58.898 --> 33:00.092
when we went out
the other night.

33:00.166 --> 33:01.360
Anyway, I was gonna...

33:01.434 --> 33:03.595
you know, come by and drop off
some soup or something...

33:03.670 --> 33:05.934
so, um, maybe I'll see you.

33:07.407 --> 33:09.773
# Shine, let it shine #

33:09.842 --> 33:13.073
# Even if it burns your eyes #

33:13.146 --> 33:15.842
# This light of mine is mine #

33:15.915 --> 33:17.678
- # And I'm gonna let it shine #
- It's Henry.

33:17.750 --> 33:20.548
The sandwich was gone, so,
you know, that's a good sign.

33:20.620 --> 33:21.917
Buying a sandwich for someone...

33:21.988 --> 33:23.148
you've never
had a sandwich with...

33:23.222 --> 33:24.484
is a lot harder than you think.

33:24.557 --> 33:25.956
I mean, just the bread.

33:26.025 --> 33:27.492
I started off
with whole wheat...

33:27.560 --> 33:29.528
but then I worried that,
you know, I'm saying...

33:29.595 --> 33:31.028
you're kind
of a crunchy person...

33:31.097 --> 33:32.758
who only eats whole wheat.

33:32.832 --> 33:35.323
I almost went with pumpernickel,
but then I'd look like...

33:35.401 --> 33:36.891
the kind of guy
who wants to impose...

33:36.969 --> 33:39.301
my weird bread fetish
on everyone and...

33:39.372 --> 33:42.034
You know, now, I'm one of those
idiots who just prattles on...

33:42.108 --> 33:43.598
in, uh, answering machines...

33:45.078 --> 33:46.875
and also uses a word
like "prattles."

33:48.081 --> 33:50.447
So the only thing I can think of
is that, uh, you really just...

33:50.516 --> 33:51.778
you don't
wanna talk to me anymore.

33:52.885 --> 33:56.480
Um, if that's right,
well, um...

33:56.556 --> 33:57.921
I don't know, I guess just...

33:57.990 --> 33:59.651
kinda keep doin'
what you're doin'.

34:01.260 --> 34:03.660
- # Shine, let it shine #
- So, take care of yourself...

34:03.730 --> 34:06.824
- # Even if it burns your eyes #
- Ashley.

34:06.899 --> 34:09.458
# This light of mine is mine #

34:09.534 --> 34:11.900
# And I'm gonna let it shine #

34:12.871 --> 34:14.396
There you are.

34:14.474 --> 34:15.600
Why have you been avoiding
my brother?

34:15.675 --> 34:17.335
Uh, I can explain.

34:17.409 --> 34:18.467
Um...

34:22.748 --> 34:24.080
I guess I can't explain.

34:24.150 --> 34:25.139
Okay,
if you didn't wanna do this...

34:25.217 --> 34:26.185
you should've just said so...

34:26.252 --> 34:27.378
but to lead him on
and let him think...

34:27.453 --> 34:29.080
that you can help him
and then just disappear?

34:29.822 --> 34:31.585
I mean, he's worse off,
if that's possible.

34:31.657 --> 34:32.715
I just couldn't do it anymore,
all right?

34:32.792 --> 34:33.759
I'm sorry.

34:33.826 --> 34:35.157
Please tell him I'm sorry.

34:35.228 --> 34:36.388
Did you run out of things
to say?

34:36.462 --> 34:37.429
- No, it's not that. It's not that.
- Because I have...

34:37.496 --> 34:38.464
- It's not...
- more information.

34:38.531 --> 34:39.964
I have letters
and some pictures and...

34:40.032 --> 34:41.623
- Is that her?
- Yeah, that's Kate.

34:47.072 --> 34:48.563
Oh, God!

34:48.641 --> 34:49.608
Wait, what do...
What does that mean?

34:49.675 --> 34:51.438
Do... Do you want the letters?

34:51.511 --> 34:54.309
All right, show's over.

34:55.415 --> 34:57.315
Come out. I know who you are...

34:57.383 --> 34:58.350
Kate.

34:58.418 --> 34:59.680
- Boo.
- God.

35:00.586 --> 35:03.521
God, it's really you.
This is unbelievable.

35:03.589 --> 35:05.113
- Are you really like a...
- Ghost?

35:06.092 --> 35:07.320
It's the only way
I can explain it.

35:07.393 --> 35:08.621
That is awesome.

35:09.562 --> 35:10.961
Here, catch.

35:15.201 --> 35:16.168
Nice throw.

35:16.235 --> 35:17.327
Crap.

35:18.438 --> 35:20.235
Hey, what was that
the other day, man?

35:20.306 --> 35:22.467
I was just trying to help out
the situation.

35:22.542 --> 35:23.509
Help?

35:23.576 --> 35:25.203
You were helping yourself
to Henry.

35:26.479 --> 35:27.503
Okay, so, like, I'm like...

35:27.580 --> 35:29.775
I'm like
slightly attracted to him.

35:29.849 --> 35:30.941
Well, he's not right for you.

35:31.017 --> 35:32.177
Yes, he is.

35:32.251 --> 35:35.982
He is considerate, and
he is sweet, and, you know...

35:36.055 --> 35:37.955
pulls the chair out for me
when I sit.

35:38.024 --> 35:38.991
Big deal.

35:39.058 --> 35:40.753
It is a big deal,
and you know it, okay?

35:40.827 --> 35:42.522
He's been wonderful to me
from the second he met me...

35:42.595 --> 35:44.290
even though he probably thought
I was a little crazy.

35:44.363 --> 35:45.330
Well, you do
talk to dead people.

35:45.398 --> 35:46.365
That's a little crazy.

35:46.432 --> 35:47.626
Oh, I'm crazy?

35:47.700 --> 35:50.464
You're the one who's spying
on me in the frickin' shower.

35:51.504 --> 35:54.098
You're right.
I'm sorry about that.

35:54.173 --> 35:57.540
You know what, girl to girl,
you're gettin' a little hippy.

35:57.610 --> 35:59.168
You might wanna cut back
on the pasta.

36:01.247 --> 36:02.236
All right, what do you want?

36:02.315 --> 36:04.374
I'm serious. Why are you here?

36:04.450 --> 36:05.678
Look, we got off
on the wrong foot...

36:05.751 --> 36:07.582
and that's partly my fault...

36:07.653 --> 36:09.177
with the threats
from beyond and all.

36:09.255 --> 36:10.552
- Yeah.
- But here's the thing.

36:10.623 --> 36:12.853
I was sent back to earth
to protect Henry.

36:12.925 --> 36:14.790
Really? How do you know that?

36:14.861 --> 36:18.126
Because when you die,
you go to this white room...

36:18.197 --> 36:21.894
and there's a woman who may
or may not be an angel...

36:21.968 --> 36:26.428
and she says that, you know,
just, you know...

36:26.506 --> 36:28.337
stuff, and I just know.

36:29.909 --> 36:32.434
So, like, I have to like
stay away from Henry now?

36:32.512 --> 36:35.106
Oh, that would be so great.
Thank you.

36:37.183 --> 36:38.741
Wait a second.
Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait.

36:38.818 --> 36:40.251
But you're dead.

36:40.319 --> 36:41.877
I still don't want you
to see him.

36:41.954 --> 36:43.387
Yeah, I know,
but for argument's sake...

36:43.456 --> 36:44.548
I mean,
if I wanted to see him...

36:44.624 --> 36:46.182
there's not a whole hell
of a lot you could do about it.

36:46.259 --> 36:47.283
Really?

36:47.860 --> 36:50.158
Then why have you been hiding
in your bedroom for a week?

36:51.030 --> 36:52.190
Well, I'm done hiding.

36:52.265 --> 36:53.698
Let's not let this get ugly.

36:53.766 --> 36:54.733
I think it already has.

36:54.800 --> 36:56.062
You have no idea.

36:58.971 --> 36:59.995
Ashley?

37:00.072 --> 37:01.801
Hi, Henry.

37:01.874 --> 37:03.239
Oh, sorry.

37:03.309 --> 37:04.298
"Dr. Mills."

37:04.377 --> 37:06.242
Oh, hey, you're alive.

37:06.312 --> 37:07.677
Yeah, thanks to you.

37:10.349 --> 37:11.373
You're a real lifesaver.

37:11.450 --> 37:12.417
Know... You know,
the food that you left me...

37:12.485 --> 37:13.952
was the only thing
that kept me going.

37:14.020 --> 37:15.248
Oh, you got that. Good.

37:15.321 --> 37:16.754
I left a couple
of messages, but...

37:16.822 --> 37:18.949
I know. I'm so sorry.
I, um...

37:19.025 --> 37:21.357
I just... I felt so ill
that I couldn't talk to anyone.

37:21.427 --> 37:22.394
But the minute I felt better...

37:22.461 --> 37:24.725
I wanted to come down here
and thank you in person.

37:24.797 --> 37:26.059
I hope you're not mad at me.

37:26.132 --> 37:27.759
No, not at all. I...

37:27.833 --> 37:29.494
I'm sorry that I called
and bothered you.

37:29.569 --> 37:31.161
I mean, you said that you'd call
when you felt better...

37:31.237 --> 37:32.795
and here you are.

37:32.872 --> 37:34.271
Do you wanna go out tonight?

37:38.044 --> 37:39.909
Yeah. All right. I'd love to.

37:39.979 --> 37:41.537
Okay, great.

37:41.614 --> 37:43.104
Oh, great. Oh, great.

37:43.182 --> 37:45.616
I'll let you get back
to saving animals' lives...

37:45.685 --> 37:47.209
and everything.

37:47.286 --> 37:48.446
Okay.

37:57.396 --> 37:59.125
And what seems to be
the trouble with Margaret?

37:59.198 --> 38:00.597
Itchy ass.

38:00.666 --> 38:01.860
Excellent.

